2007-02-23  Miloslav Trmac  <mitr@redhat.com>

	* configure.in: Version 0.56.1.
	* NEWS: Update.

	* tests/files_test.py (Tests.testUserSetpass3)
	(Tests.testGroupLookupName2, Tests.testGroupSetpass3): Simplify the
	lambda expression.

