	* python/misc.c (libuser_prompt_destroy): Use PyObject_DEL since
	we allocated with PyObject_NEW (#220679)
	* python/ent.c (libuser_entity_destroy): Likewise.
	* python/admin.c (libuser_admin_destroy): Likewise.

