	specifies a nonexistent group name.  Use the specified user ID.
	* apps/lnewusers.1: Update.

	* apps/luseradd.c (main): Actually implement -p and -P.

	* apps/lusermod.c (main): Fix ignoring of other changes when one
	of -p, -P, -L, -U is used.

